snippet.title: EPIC LOON - VHS tapes ruined this man's life!!!
snippet.description:
http://www.epicloon.com
https://twitter.com/Epic_Loon
---------------------------------------------------------------------
I bet when you first saw this, you were all like 'Ewww this is such CLICKBAIT! Just look at that title! These guys are grade A, top shelf yet somehow also bottom-of-the-barrel marketing buffoons!' Well...what do you think now? You ended up watching a very strange trailer for a pretty badass looking game. It's got aliens and everything. Are we cool now? No hard feelings? What are you doing later tonight? We're not busy, so if you wanted to hang out...

EPIC LOON! Coming to PC, PS4 and Xbox One in early 2018! 
---------------------------------------------------------------------
Music by Pryapisme
Special thanks to Léo CAPOU, Duffy WEBER and Florent RENUIT Grandma house
